casts.text:
today is the last day of my crowdfund for devconnect.

all my life i’ve done everything not to ask for help.
i found my first job at 15, built my own path, carried my own boxes, moved apartments alone. i kept proving to myself i could handle everything. not anymore.

since 2023 i’ve been carving out a new path in web3, creating, teaching, building something of my own. this crowdfund is the first time i’ve ever asked for help.

if you’ve enjoyed my videos and the content i’ve been bringing to this space, this is your chance to help me take it further.
your support today,  big or small can help me bring back daily stories, videos, and interviews from argentina.

thank you for supporting me.

Get in touch if you’d like to do this.
